The evidence with the title 'Mental health: there's an app for that : Nature News & Comment ' says Apr 6, 2016  ... Estimates suggest that about 29 % of people will experience a mental disorder in their lifetime . Data from the World Health Organization (WHO) show that many of those people — up to 55 % in developed countries and 85 % in developing ones — are not getting the treatment they need . Mobile health apps  ... 
